data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Sandpiper Bay Golf Community, just minutes away from the breathtaking Sunset Beach. This spacious single-family residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and elegance. As you step into this one-level haven, you are greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the spacious living area, formal dining room, and the heart of the home--a kitchen with modern appliances and ample counter space perfect for entertaining. Natural light pours in through the large windows throughout the home.This residence boasts three bedrooms, including an owner's suite that is a true retreat. The en suite bathroom is equipped with a separate tub and shower, creating a spa-like experience for the lucky homeowner. Enjoy picturesque views of the manicured golf course and serene pond from multiple vantage points, including a charming sunroom--a perfect spot to unwind and soak in the beauty of your surroundings. The gas fireplace in the living area adds a touch of coziness, making it an ideal spot to gather on cooler evenings.This residence is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. The Sandpiper Bay Golf Community offers an exclusive owner's clubhouse complete with a fitness room, inviting pool, and stunning pond views. It's the perfect place to meet neighbors, stay active, and enjoy the beauty of coastal living.Situated in close proximity to the Sandpiper Bay Clubhouse and it's 27 hole scenic golf course, local shopping, restaurants, and the pristine Sunset Beach, this property offers the ideal combination of luxury and convenience. Don't miss the chance to call this beautiful home yours--a sanctuary where comfort, style, and community come together in perfect harmony.
